{"tid":1657926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港全民議政會》籌備近一個月工作報告","createTime":"2019-10-16T10:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T23:19:50.000Z","uid":300718,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ace5dfc94ce9960855ec6c019b39488fb3de9298","tid":1657926,"uid":300718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"加入：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">投票及公佈Channel： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=410244e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkassembly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkassembly&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=40c950ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkassembly</a> </span></strong></span><br />\n- - - - - <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>里程碑</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">14/9 本人就成立【民間民主平台】開第一個Post</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">19/9 【籌備工作組】正式成立</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">24/9 正式成立「香港全民議政會」Hong Kong Assembly民間民主平台 [3000人]</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">25/9 第一個投票 &ndash; Logo 1st Round (1979 votes)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">27/9 第二個投票 &ndash; 首投預備投票 (5934 votes) [6000人]</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">8/10 第三個投票 &ndash; 緊急法 + 禁蒙面法 + Logo 2nd Round (4864 votes)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10/10 第四個投票 &ndash; 公安條例 (7567 votes)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">14/10 第五個投票 &ndash; 立法會黃色保安警示 (on-going)</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>主要工作</strong></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">成立工作組 (100%)<br />\n&gt;策略、文宣、IT、議政、投票、Telegram Admin小組正運作並推進平台</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">命名及選出Logo (100%)<br />\n&gt;正式成立「香港全民議政會」，開展宣傳及工作</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">宣傳及推人數 (&gt;9500 人, on-going)<br />\n&gt;於以下渠道宣傳: LIHKG (7 official posts)、Facebook、Instagram 、Twitter、Telegram</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">開展Stage 1 簡易投票 (5次, on-going)<br />\n&gt;透過將立法會處理的法案進行再投票，讓全民議政<br />\n&gt;在Stage 2前進行Testing、保持熱度及增加人數</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">籌備Stage 2 最簡易可行之民主平台 (60%)<br />\n&gt;「香港全民議政會」的【Product】是【民間民主平台】。我們正預備一個有「動議議案」、「和議議案」和「議案投票」基本功能的Minimum Viable Product作為第一代的【民間民主平台】，讓議民實踐民主、測試並優化平台、引導方向<br />\n&gt;議民對平台的運作作出回饋，同時IT組觀察並按需要增加功能，以發展更完善的【Product】</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">籌備Stage 3 網頁版民主平台 (10%)<br />\n&gt;因預計進階版的【民間民主平台】應為網頁版，正積極研究及籌備</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">長遠目標<br />\n&gt;請參考以下About Us</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>關於香港全民議政會</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我們的願景是在香港建立真正符合民主理念的政治體制，以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「實踐民主來爭取民主」</strong></span>為理念。<br />\n<br />\n為此，香港全民議政會希望透過搭建一個 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主議政平台</strong></span>；讓全民皆有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「提案權」</strong></span>，並於該議案取得<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>足夠和議後付諸公投</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n以達至以下目的：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>實踐政治平等精神</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;保障不同政見的議民皆享同等的表達和被聆聽權利，並能平等議政。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>養成公民參與風氣</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;推動全民議政；發展公民社會。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">讓民意發揮力量</span></strong><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;提供可信的發聲平台，滙聚民意；整合並定期向公眾發佈；促使議員反映真正民意，發揮其監察及約制政權的應有效用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>實踐民主制度</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;試驗真正符合民主精神的議政制度，再由全民協力逐步完善；為香港尋找可行的民主運作方法。<br />\n<br />\n- - - - - <br />\n加入：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">投票及公佈Channel： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=410244e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkassembly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkassembly&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=40c950ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkassembly</a> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0bd1c56fb4805b68f51c002367b062a11835fa5d","tid":1657926,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"6ad190c63cc6e73ca6525bb25d8adcb4b6d89dd1","tid":1657926,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc6309bd4a8bcc635b8b1c2d0856328e5070302","tid":1657926,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da382e615782dbca9671ff819d4fde1ece4cb340","tid":1657926,"uid":281252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"推，加油"},{"pid":"d95b833a0877ab0db157ec1c52cebb0ca8fb00cc","tid":1657926,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府都唔理你嫁啦，搞乜鬼，定你想起大台，遲啲叫人投票休唔休息，衝唔衝擊"},{"pid":"443fab9f527b64087d8f6a7100234c2c74a26501","tid":1657926,"uid":114252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70d6d635f134e98a71ff995df98498869779133a","tid":1657926,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:12:15.000Z","m